OL,3,CLiverpool legend Sir Kenny Dalglish
OL,4,Creveals cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FLiverpool legend Sir Kenny Dalglish
OL,7,Fhas revealed he is undergoing
OL,8,Ftreatment for cancer.
OL,10,FThe 75-year-old former Scotland,
OL,11,FCeltic and Liverpool great was moved
OL,12,Fto issue a statement after mistakenly
OL,13,Fposting on social media.
OL,15,F"As my inadvertent social media post
OL,16,Fhas indicated, I am currently
OL,17,Fundergoing treatment for cancer," said
OL,18,FDalglish.
OL,20,F"Unlike my mobile phone use, the
OL,21,Ftreatment is going well.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@aO]|D@AOU
