FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780402267
OL,3,CLiverpool legend Sir Kenny Dalglish
OL,4,Creveals cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"Ideally, this would have remained
OL,7,Fprivate because that's the way it
OL,8,Fshould be, but my useless technology
OL,9,Fskills have forced my hand.
OL,11,F"Obviously I did not mean to make this
OL,12,Fmatter public so I would appreciate it
OL,13,Fif the privacy of my family and myself
OL,14,Fare respected.
OL,16,F"As ever, thank you to the wonderful
OL,17,Fmedical staff who have shown
OL,18,Fincredible care and discretion, not
OL,19,Fjust for me but for many, many others.
OL,20,FThey are a credit to themselves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@aO]
