OL,3,CLiverpool legend Sir Kenny Dalglish
OL,4,Creveals cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FSir Kenny helped the Reds win multiple
OL,7,Fleague titles and European Cups as a
OL,8,Fplayer and later returned as a manager.
OL,10,FDalglish's former club Liverpool, for
OL,11,Fwhom he played and managed, sent their
OL,12,F"support, best wishes and love".
OL,14,FThey added: "The club would also like
OL,15,Fto underscore his request for privacy
OL,16,Fmoving forward."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@_O]
